imishinga imwe nimwe ishyira ho ibikorwa byayo byihariye

381
00:21:01,033 --> 00:21:04,056
byo gushyira hamwe umutungo mu bushoramari.

382
00:21:04,056 --> 00:21:08,780
gusa indi mishinga ntigira igikorwa nkicyo,

383
00:21:08,780 --> 00:21:11,694
ahubwo bakora ubushoramari kubera izindi mamvu zihariye,

384
00:21:11,694 --> 00:21:13,873
gusa iyo mishinga imara igihe cyirekire

385
00:21:13,873 --> 00:21:16,496
mbere yo guhitamo icyo gukora.

386
00:21:16,496 --> 00:21:19,411
kurundi ruhande, igihe fatizo

387
00:21:19,411 --> 00:21:21,692
giterwa nimbaraga zuwo mushinga munini.

388
00:21:21,692 --> 00:21:24,873
bishobora kuva ku myaka umunani kugeza kumyaka icumi mugihe wihangana,

389
00:21:24,873 --> 00:21:27,020
wihangana cyane muri rusange.

390
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:29,592
kandi nanone bigaterwa n' intego ubwo bushoramari bufite

391
00:21:29,592 --> 00:21:31,674
bugendeye kuri gahunda y' umushinga.

392
00:21:31,674 --> 00:21:35,354
nimba bifuza ko amafaranga yabo agaruka.

393
00:21:35,354 --> 00:21:37,737
ubwo rero bifuza cyane kubona umusozo,

394
00:21:37,737 --> 00:21:40,592
bakazagira igihe fatizo gisa na kimwe cy' abakusanije umutungo.

395
00:21:40,592 --> 00:21:44,122
kurundi ruhande, nimba bifuza kugaruza umutungo mubundi buryo.

396
00:21:44,122 --> 00:21:48,239
muyandi magambo, umushinga wawe ugiye kuzamura ibyiza 

397
00:21:48,239 --> 00:21:51,479
bizatuma ibyo ucuruza bigurrwa cyane .

398
00:21:51,479 --> 00:21:53,583
bashobora kubasha kwihanganira igihe cyirekire

399
00:21:53,583 --> 00:21:57,313
mbere yuko bagerageza kwambura amafaranga umushinga wawe.

400
00:21:57,313 --> 00:22:01,677
igihe fatizo gishobora kuba kirekire kugeza ku myaka icumi wihangana

401
00:22:01,677 --> 00:22:05,197
mbere yuko banibaza cyane  

402
00:22:05,197 --> 00:22:09,053
uko bava mu mushinga nk' abashoramari.

403
00:22:09,053 --> 00:22:10,622
ubwo nizihe nyungu zirimo?

404
00:22:10,622 --> 00:22:12,166
harimo inyungu nyinshi cyane.

405
00:22:12,166 --> 00:22:14,300
bashobora kuba abaguzi bawe bakomeye cg se abo urangura ho.

406
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:16,628
mugihe babaye abaguzi bawe,

407
00:22:16,628 --> 00:22:20,222
bashobora kwibaza ko nugurisha byinshi,

408
00:22:20,222 --> 00:22:22,944
nabo baza kugurisha ho byinshi.

409
00:22:22,944 --> 00:22:24,362
rero iyo ishobora kuba inyungu nini.

410
00:22:24,362 --> 00:22:26,783
ibigutera imbaraga ni byiza kandi k' umurongo murubwo buryo

411
00:22:26,783 --> 00:22:28,668
cyangwa se uwo urangura ashobora kuba umwe.

412
00:22:28,668 --> 00:22:32,642
akenshi ntago bakunze kwihutishwa no gusoza nkuko nabivuze hano

413
00:22:32,642 --> 00:22:37,662
uretse igihe bashishikajwe cyane nigaruka ry' amafaranga ava mu mushinga wawe

414
00:22:37,662 --> 00:22:42,308
cyane ko ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwagaragaje ko atari igitekerezo cyiza

415
00:22:42,308 --> 00:22:46,286
kandi akenshi ntibakunze gutera imbere unagendeye kubyo imishinga ikomeye ivuga.

416
00:22:46,286 --> 00:22:50,338
byaba byiza ushatse umushinga ucyeneye inyungu mu

417
00:22:50,338 --> 00:22:53,992
bushoramari bw' umwuga bitanfukanye n' ubushoramari bw' amafaranga,

418
00:22:53,992 --> 00:22:56,458
kandi ibyo nabyo bizagufasha no kuruhande rw' igihe fatizo

419
00:22:56,458 --> 00:23:00,677
kubera ko batazakwihutisha cyane mu kugerageza kandi bagufashe neza kugeza ugurishije.

420
00:23:02,624 --> 00:23:04,325
ingaruka mbi.

421
00:23:04,325 --> 00:23:06,187
ugomba kureka ubuyobozi bumwe.

422
00:23:06,187 --> 00:23:09,675
bazajya bagira ibyo bahindura kubyemezo ufata

423
00:23:09,675 --> 00:23:13,724
kandi gukomeza imbaraga zabo

424
00:23:13,724 --> 00:23:18,012
kubyemezo ufata nuburyo bwo kwihutisha ibyemezo byabo.

425
00:23:18,012 --> 00:23:22,185
abantu bamwe bihutira kuza mu mishinga itangira kubera ko bashaka gufata ibyemezo byihuse

426
00:23:22,185 --> 00:23:25,359
hamwe nimishinga minini cyane cyane iyi mishinga ishobora 

427
00:23:25,359 --> 00:23:29,118
ubu bushoramari bwa miliyoni 10$ mu mishinga mito

428
00:23:29,118 --> 00:23:33,159
ikanagira igihe gito cyo gufata ibyemezo.

429
00:23:33,159 --> 00:23:34,839
ibyo nabyo ugomba kubitekereza ho

430
00:23:34,839 --> 00:23:37,240
kubera ko iyo ushaka gukora ikintu kandi vuba vuba,

431
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:39,042
bashobora kuba batakiteguye.

432
00:23:39,042 --> 00:23:43,764
bishobora kubafata igihe kirekire cyo gufata ibyemezo no kubyemeza mu mushinga wabo munini.

433
00:23:44,890 --> 00:23:48,714
ingaruka mbi ya nyuma hano nuko bitera amakimbirane mu mikorere.

434
00:23:48,714 --> 00:23:49,746
Ibyo bisobanuye iki?

435
00:23:49,746 --> 00:23:52,913
muri macye icyo ibyo bisobanura nuko mu gutangira bisa nkaho ari byiza cyane.

436
00:23:52,913 --> 00:23:55,876
bisa nkaho bikorana cyane. Ni byiza cyane.

437
00:23:55,876 --> 00:24:00,565
gusa uko igihe gitambuka ubona ko inyungu z' umushinga wawe

438
00:24:00,565 --> 00:24:05,596
n' inyungu z' umushinga munini bitari neza mumurongo umwe.

439
00:24:05,596 --> 00:24:10,481
muri icyo gihe, bishobora gutuma rwiyemezo arangara

440
00:24:10,481 --> 00:24:15,314
kandi bikaba byatera ikintu gisa nk' amakimbirane hagati y' imishinga yombi.

441
00:24:15,314 --> 00:24:17,256
kandi kuva nabo harimo ibyabo,

442
00:24:17,256 --> 00:24:20,807
uzajya ukorana nabo cyane,

443
00:24:20,807 --> 00:24:25,972
maze iri kimbirane rikomeze ryiyongere, bikaba byaba ikirangaza gikomeye.

444
00:24:25,972 --> 00:24:27,640
noneho hano hari igice cya nyuma.

445
00:24:27,640 --> 00:24:33,093
ni muri macye isoko y' imfashanyo nuko bigenda.

446
00:24:34,063 --> 00:24:37,916
kandi mvuge muri macye ibyo twavuze ho byose.

447
00:24:37,916 --> 00:24:40,545
ngire ibintu bimwe bimwe bitandukanye nsubira mo.

448
00:24:40,545 --> 00:24:43,980
kur' uruhande rw' ibumoso tuhafite amasoko amwe namwe atandukanye.

449
00:24:45,158 --> 00:24:47,424
namafaranga angahe ushobora kubakuramo

450
00:24:48,026 --> 00:24:52,650
kandi ni mukihe gihe gito gishoboka ibyo byaba mo.

451
00:24:54,448 --> 00:24:57,465
ibi nabyo nashoboraga kuba nabishyira mumutuku nabyo.

452
00:24:57,465 --> 00:24:59,488
kubera ko ishobora kumara igihe kirekire cyane.

453
00:25:00,222 --> 00:25:03,233
kandi twashoboraga no gushyira ibi mu cyatsi

454
00:25:08,700 --> 00:25:11,559
kubera ko bihangane cyane kandi bakaba n' abashoramari b' umwuga.

455
00:25:11,559 --> 00:25:14,917
bafata igihe kinini.

456
00:25:15,702 --> 00:25:20,231
bashobora gufata igihe kirekire kugira ngo bafate icyemezo cyo gushorimari kuncuro ya mbere

457
00:25:20,231 --> 00:25:25,465
kandi bashobora no gufata igihe kirekire cyo kugufatira ibyemezo byawe bikomeza.

458
00:25:25,984 --> 00:25:27,001
bazaguha igishoro.

459
00:25:27,001 --> 00:25:31,403
nako aya masoko yose azaguha igishoro

460
00:25:31,403 --> 00:25:33,753
mu kuyobora umushinga wawe.

461
00:25:35,196 --> 00:25:38,311
kandi nkuko nabivuze ho, bishobora kuba byiza

462
00:25:38,311 --> 00:25:40,793
kuko ushobora kubona igishoro kiza giturutse mw' ikusanya ry' umutungo

463
00:25:40,793 --> 00:25:42,863
gusa ku rundi ruhande,

464
00:25:44,551 --> 00:25:47,677
ushobora kubona igishoro cyinshi, binashobotse cyinshi cyane,

465
00:25:47,677 --> 00:25:49,245
giturutse mw' ikusanya ry' umutungo.

466
00:25:49,863 --> 00:25:53,731
ukoranye n' ikusanya ry' umutungo, ureka ubuyobozi bwinshi warufite,

467
00:25:53,731 --> 00:25:56,393
maze bakaba aribo bakoramo cyane.

468
00:25:56,969 --> 00:25:58,521
Kurundi ruhande,

469
00:25:58,521 --> 00:26:03,064
inyungu zuko bakuvuga bitewe no gukorana n' ikusanya ry' umutungo ziba ari nziza cyane.

470
00:26:03,064 --> 00:26:06,498
mugihe wavuga ko wacyiriye ikusanya ry' umutungo,

471
00:26:07,921 --> 00:26:12,134
bifite izindi nyungu nyinshi iyo uri gukorana n' abaranguza, abagura.

472
00:26:12,134 --> 00:26:14,214
ukavuga, ndi umushinga utangira.

473
00:26:14,214 --> 00:26:17,113
mubyukuri nta mushoramari numwe mfite byose ninjye ibyikorera

474
00:26:17,113 --> 00:26:19,931
ukongera ho "ubushoramari bw' ibanze nabukuye mur' uyu mushinga."

475
00:26:21,011 --> 00:26:25,368
ibyo bishobora kugira akamaro igihe uvuga ufite nabagura babishoboye benshi.

476
00:26:29,059 --> 00:26:33,913
mugukomeza mvuga kw' ikusanya ry' umutungo hano:

477
00:26:33,913 --> 00:26:35,876
bifasha mu buryo bwo gushaka imfashanyo.

478
00:26:35,876 --> 00:26:38,083
ka nshyireho "Mwitonde cyane!"

479
00:26:39,814 --> 00:26:43,734
nashakaga kuvuga ku nyungu ndetse no kw' ikusanya ry' umutungo,

480
00:26:43,734 --> 00:26:47,172
kandi inyungu na ba rwiyemezamirimo ntago iteka bihora kumurongo umwe 100%,

481
00:26:47,172 --> 00:26:49,772
cyane cyane iyo haje mo gutera inkunga umushinga.

482
00:26:49,772 --> 00:26:52,317
gusa nyine iyo umushinga ukoze neza buri wese arishima,

483
00:26:52,317 --> 00:26:54,267
kandi aho rwose ntakibazo.

484
00:26:54,267 --> 00:26:58,604
ikibazo kimwe kiboneka iyo umushinga utabasha kugaruza

485
00:26:58,604 --> 00:27:02,518
kandi imiterere uhabwa buri gihembwe kumapuro

486
00:27:02,518 --> 00:27:04,599
ugomba kuyicunga neza cyane nubwitonzi

487
00:27:04,599 --> 00:27:06,162
kugira ngo urebe uko byagenze.

488
00:27:06,162 --> 00:27:09,082
mugihe ibintu bigenze neza cg igihe bigenze nabi,

489
00:27:09,487 --> 00:27:11,994
kandi bagiye kugira ibikorwa bafata mu mushinga wawe.

490
00:27:11,994 --> 00:27:13,814
bose bazagira umwanya wibikorwa bafata.

491
00:27:15,307 --> 00:27:18,071
gusa bazaba abashoramari bakora cyane,

492
00:27:18,071 --> 00:27:19,738
abakusanya umutungo.

493
00:27:23,662 --> 00:27:27,871
ibintu bya nyuma bitandukanye ncaka kuvuga ho n' udutsiko dutanga inkunga.

494
00:27:30,431 --> 00:27:32,387
ushobora kugira abashoramari benshi,

495
00:27:35,176 --> 00:27:39,093
nkuko navuze udustiko, ntago bakora hamwe mu mushinga umwe.

496
00:27:39,093 --> 00:27:42,839
nabantu bikorera ku giti cyabo rero bakaba bashobora gukorana n' abashoramari benshi

497
00:27:43,444 --> 00:27:45,017
Kurundi ruhande,

498
00:27:46,007 --> 00:27:49,547
bashobora kukugira inama atari gusa mu buryo bwo gutanga inkunga

499
00:27:49,547 --> 00:27:51,819
ahubwo no mubyemezo by' imiyoborere,

500
00:27:51,819 --> 00:27:54,385
kandi bakanaguha isura nziza.

501
00:27:54,385 --> 00:27:57,241
nimba ushobora kuvuga, ko wakiriye ubushoramari buturutse ku gatsiko gatera inkunga.

502
00:27:57,241 --> 00:28:01,543
ibyo bishobora gufatwa nkibifite inyungu mugihe uri gushaka kumvikana nabandi bafatanyabikorwa.

503
00:28:03,112 --> 00:28:05,840
ubwigenge, nkuko nabivuze ho, ugomba kureka

504
00:28:05,840 --> 00:28:06,830
bimwe mubyo wayoboraga uko bya genda kose.

505
00:28:06,830 --> 00:28:09,382
ushobora kuba ureka akenshi mu bijyanye no gufata ibyemezo

506
00:28:09,382 --> 00:28:11,888
mugihe wacyireye ubushoramari buturutse kubakusanya umutungo.

507
00:28:11,888 --> 00:28:14,864
kandi ku bijyanye no gutandukana nkuko nabivuze ho mu ntagiriro--

508
00:28:14,864 --> 00:28:16,431
ntakintu nigeze nandika hano

509
00:28:16,431 --> 00:28:19,747
kubera ko ubusanzwe aya masoko yose

510
00:28:19,747 --> 00:28:25,737
atandukanye cyane nikipe yawe isanzwe,

511
00:28:25,737 --> 00:28:27,077
ikipe watangiranye nayo.

512
00:28:27,077 --> 00:28:29,407
ntahanu na hamwe muhuriye.

513
00:28:29,407 --> 00:28:31,929
ntago ukorana nabo igihe cyose, nibindi.

514
00:28:31,929 --> 00:28:34,442
rero harimo itandukaniro rigaragara

515
00:28:34,442 --> 00:28:38,116
kandi bagomba kwitonda cyane kubera gukora cyane

516
00:28:38,116 --> 00:28:40,135
kandi bishobora kumara igihe.

517
00:28:40,135 --> 00:28:42,344
bazakora ubunetsi mu mushinga wawe,

518
00:28:42,344 --> 00:28:44,300
imiterere y' umushinga, imipango y' umushinga.

519
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:46,910
maze bahite mo badahamya neza

